title: Dragon Ball NORDIC Collection (NO/SV/FI/DK/IS)
description:
This collection contains seven of the "Dragon Ball Z" movies released in scandinavian countries in 2004. These are out of production and almost impossible to obtain. There are four more released movies missing, but as I have failed to obtain them, I'm not able to upload them. Enjoy, seed and comment like true gentlemen!

Age Rating: 11 years and older
Runtime: 50 minutes each film
Audio: Japanese, Norwegian, Swedish, Danish, Finnish
Subtitles: Norwegian, Swedish, Danish, Finnish. (Islandic: Movie 2&3 ONLY)
Size: About 1GB each movie
File Format: .mkv

NOTE: Due to problems with splitting the files, Movie 2 and 3 are invidual files. [Nordic] is the dubbed version with a Norwegian, Danish, Swedish and Finnish voice track, while [JAPANESE] features the original japanese voice track with subtitles.
